@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
}

<div class="card shadow-sm p-4">
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-primary">Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>
        MediLink is committed to protecting your personal and healthcare information.
        We respect your privacy and ensure that your data is handled securely and responsibly.
    </p>

    <p>
        Any information collected on this platform, such as personal details, appointments,
        and medical data, is used only to provide and improve our healthcare services.
        We do not share your information with third parties unless required by law.
    </p>

    <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized
        access, loss, or misuse. Access to information is limited to authorized users only,
        including patients, doctors, and administrators.
    </p>

    <p>
        By using MediLink, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance
        with this policy. If you have any concerns about your privacy, please contact the
        system administrator.
    </p>
</div>